Class TypedValueStringMapper

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<Type,StringMapper>
public class TypedValueStringMapper
extends HashMap<Type,StringMapper>

Handles mapping Java objects to Strings and back. Intended for short, human-readable Strings (unlike the Serializable infrastructure, or an XML mapping, etc. Hence, limited to simple types.
